oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hatch Show Print C. O. D. and All Charges (black)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Hatch Show Print (Firm); Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative featuring a COD (cash on delivery) and all charges template, which Hatch Show Print would have used when sending out rush advertising matter. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
